\c 11
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* ithembisa ukubapha inyama
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi abantu besola kwakukubi endlebeni zeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Dute. 9.22.\x*. Kwathi iN\nd kosi\nd* isikuzwile, ulaka lwayo lwavutha\x + Hlab. 78.21.\x*, lomlilo weN\nd kosi\nd* wavutha phakathi kwabo, waqothula emngceleni wenkamba\x + Levi 10.2. Nani 16.35. 2 Kho. 1.12. Hlab. 106.18.\x*.
\v 2 Abantu basebekhala kuMozisi; uMozisi wasekhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lomlilo wadeda\x + Gen. 20.17. Jak. 5.16.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho wabiza ibizo laleyondawo iTabera, ngoba umlilo weN\nd kosi\nd* wavutha phakathi kwabo.
\p
\v 4 Ududu lwabantu olwaluphakathi kwabo lwaloyisa isiloyiso\x + Eks. 12.38.\x*; ngakho labantwana bakoIsrayeli baphinde bakhala inyembezi, bathi: Ngubani ozasipha inyama ukuthi sidle\x + Hlab. 106.14. Hlab. 78.18. 1 Kor. 10.6.\x*?
\v 5 Siyazikhumbula inhlanzi esasizidla ngesihle eGibhithe, amakhomane, lamakhabe, lamaliki, lesandindima, legalikhi\x + Eks. 16.3. Nani 21.5. Seb. 7.39.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa khathesi umphefumulo wethu womile, kakulalutho ngitsho, ngaphandle kwale imana \add phambi\add* kwamehlo ethu.
\v 7 Njalo imana yayinjengenhlanyelo \w yekhoriyanderi\w**\x + Eks. 16.14,31.\x*, lokukhangeleka kwayo kwakunjengokukhangeleka \w kwebedola\w**\x + Gen. 2.12.\x*.
\v 8 Abantu bahambahamba bayibutha\x + 2 Sam. 24.2,8.\x* bayichola ematsheni okuchola, loba bayigiga engigeni, bayipheka ezimbizeni, benza amaqebelengwana ngayo; lokunambitheka kwayo kwakunjengokunambitheka komhluzi wamafutha\x + Hlab. 32.4; Eks. 16.31.\x*.
\v 9 Lapho amazolo esehlela phezu kwenkamba ebusuku, imana yehla phezu kwawo\x + Eks. 16.13,14.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Njalo uMozisi wezwa abantu bekhala inyembezi ngokwensapho zabo, ngulowo lalowo emnyango wethente lakhe. Lolaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwavutha kakhulu; futhi kwaba kubi emehlweni kaMozisi\x + 11.1.\x*.
\v 11 UMozisi wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Wenzeleni okubi encekwini yakho? Njalo kungani ngingatholanga umusa emehlweni akho ukuthi ubeke umthwalo walababantu bonke phezu kwami?\x + Dute. 1.12.\x*
\v 12 Mina ngakhulelwa yibo bonke lababantu yini? Kumbe mina ngabazala yini, ukuze uthi kimi: Basingathe esifubeni sakho\x + Isa. 40.11.\x*, njengomlizane owesilisa esingatha umntwana omunyayo\x + Isa. 49.23; 1 Thes. 2.7.\x*, kuze kube selizweni owalifungela oyise?\x + Gen. 50.24. Eks. 13.5.\x*
\v 13 Ngingayithatha ngaphi inyama ukuthi ngibaphe bonke lababantu? Ngoba bayakhala inyembezi kimi besithi: Siphe inyama ukuze sidle\x + 2 Kho. 7.2. Mat. 15.33. Mark. 8.4. Joha. 6.7,9.\x*.
\v 14 Mina kangilamandla okuthwala bonke lababantu ngedwa, ngoba kunzima kakhulu kimi\x + Eks. 18.18.\x*.
\v 15 Uba-ke usenza njalo kimi, ake ungibulale lokungibulala, uba ngithole umusa emehlweni akho\x + 1 Kho. 19.4. Jona 4.3.\x*, njalo kangingaboni usizi lwami\x + Zef. 3.15.\x*.
\p
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Buthela kimi amadoda angamatshumi ayisikhombisa abadala bakoIsrayeli, owaziyo ngawo ukuthi angabadala babantu\x + Eks. 24.1,9.\x* lenduna zabo\x + Dute. 1.15; 16.18. Eks. 5.6,10,14,15,19.\x*, uwalethe ethenteni lenhlangano ukuze eme khona lawe.
\v 17 Njalo ngizakwehla, ngikhulume lawe khona\x + 11.25; 12.5. Gen. 11.5; 18.21. Eks. 3.8; 19.20.\x*; ngizagodla okomoya ophezu kwakho ngikufake phezu kwabo\x + Gen. 27.36. Tshu. 2.10. Nani 11.25; 1 Sam. 10.6,10; 19.20,21. 2 Kho. 2.15. Neh. 9.20.\x*; njalo bazathwala kanye lawe umthwalo wabantu, ukuze ungawuthwali wedwa\x + Eks. 18.22.\x*.
\v 18 Tshono-ke ebantwini \add uthi\add*: Zingcweliseleleni ikusasa\x + Eks. 19.10.\x*, lizakudla inyama; ngoba likhalile inyembezi endlebeni zeN\nd kosi\nd* lisithi: Ngubani ozasipha inyama ukuze sidle? Ngoba kwakukuhle kithi eGibhithe\x + 11.5.\x*. Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* izalipha inyama njalo lidle.
\v 19 Kaliyikudla usuku olulodwa, loba insuku ezimbili, loba insuku ezinhlanu, loba insuku ezilitshumi, kumbe insuku ezingamatshumi amabili,
\v 20 kuze kube yinyanga yonke, ize iphume emakhaleni enu, ilitshiphele, ngenxa yokuthi liyalile iN\nd kosi\nd* ephakathi kwenu\x + Hlab. 78.29; 106.15.\x*, lakhala inyembezi phambi kwayo lisithi: Kanti saphumelani eGibhithe?\x + 21.5.\x*
\v 21 Kodwa uMozisi wathi: Abantu abahamba ngenyawo engiphakathi kwabo bazinkulungwane ezingamakhulu ayisithupha; wena-ke uthe: Ngizabanika inyama ukuze badle inyanga yonke\x + Eks. 12.37. Eks. 38.26. Nani 1.46.\x*.
\v 22 Bazahlatshelwa izimvu lezinkomo yini ukuze zibanele?\x + Hlu. 21.14. Levi 25.26.\x* Loba bazabuthelwa yini inhlanzi zonke zolwandle ukuze zibanele?\x + Hlu. 21.14. Levi 25.26.\x*
\v 23 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sifinyeziwe yini?\x + Isa. 50.2; 59.1.\x* Khathesi uzabona ukuthi ilizwi lami lizakwenzeka kuwe kumbe hatshi\x + 23.19. Hez. 12.25; 24.14.\x*.
\p
\v 24 UMozisi wasephuma, wabatshela abantu amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd*; wabutha amadoda angamatshumi ayisikhombisa ebadaleni babantu, wawamisa ehanqe ithente\x + 11.16.\x*.
\v 25 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisehla ngeyezi\x + 11.17.\x*, yakhuluma kuye, yagodla okomoya ophezu kwakhe, yakubeka phezu kwamadoda angamatshumi ayisikhombisa, abadala. Kwasekusithi lapho uMoya ehlala phezu kwabo\x + 11.17.\x*, baprofetha, kodwa kabakuphindanga.
\v 26 Njalo kwakusele amadoda amabili enkambeni, ibizo lenye lalinguElidadi lebizo lenye linguMedadi; loMoya wahlala phezu kwawo. Njalo ayephakathi kwalabo ababhaliweyo, kodwa kawaphumanga ukuya ethenteni, njalo aprofetha enkambeni\x + 1 Sam. 20.26. Jer. 36.5.\x*.
\v 27 Kwagijima ijaha labika kuMozisi lathi: UElidadi loMedadi bayaprofetha enkambeni.
\v 28 UJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + Eks. 24.13. Nani 13.8,16.\x*, inceku kaMozisi, omunye wabatsha bakhe\x + 1 Sam. 24.2.\x*, wasephendula wathi: Nkosi yami, Mozisi, benqabele\x + Mark. 9.38. Luka 9.49.\x*.
\v 29 Kodwa uMozisi wathi kuye: Ulobukhwele ngenxa yami yini? Kungathi bonke abantu beN\nd kosi\nd* bangaba ngabaprofethi, ukuze iN\nd kosi\nd* ifake uMoya wayo phezu kwabo\x + 1 Kor. 14.5.\x*!
\v 30 UMozisi wasezibuthela enkambeni, yena labadala bakoIsrayeli.
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* ibapha izagwaca
\p
\v 31 Kwasekusuka umoya ovela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, waletha izagwaca zivela elwandle, wazehlisela phezu kwenkamba, phose uhambo losuku ngapha, njalo phose uhambo losuku ngapha, zizingelezele inkamba, njalo okungaba zingalo ezimbili phezu komhlabathi\x + Eks. 16.13. Hlab. 78.26-28; 105.40.\x*.
\v 32 Abantu basebesukuma lolosuku lonke, lobusuku bonke, losuku lonke olulandelayo, bebutha izagwaca. Lowo owayelezinlutshwana wayebuthe \w amahomeri\w** alitshumi\x + Hez. 45.11. Eks. 16.16,32,33,36.\x*; bazichayela zona inhlangothi zonke zenkamba.
\v 33 Inyama isesephakathi kwamazinyo abo ingakahlafunwa, intukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yabavuthela abantu, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yabatshaya abantu ngenhlupheko enkulu kakhulu\x + Hlab. 78.30,31.\x*.
\v 34 Ngakho ibizo laleyondawo lathiwa yiKibirothi-Hathava, ngoba lapho bangcwaba abantu abakhanukayo.
\v 35 Abantu basuka eKibirothi-Hathava baya eHazerothi; bahlala eHazerothi\x + 33.17.\x*.